82 C531.831,79.965 532.853,80.001 541,80.001 C549.148,80.001 550.169,79.965 553.369,79.82 C556.562,79.673 558.743,79.167 560.652,78.425 C562.623,77.658 564.297,76.634 565.965,74.965 C567.633,73.296 568.659,71.625 569.425,69.651 C570.167,67.743 570.674,65.562 570.82,62.369 C570.966,59.17 571,58.147 571,50 C571,41.851 570.966,40.831 570.82,37.631"></path></g></g></g></svg></div> <div style="padding-top: 8px;"> <div style=" color:#3897f0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:550; line-height:18px;"> View this post on Instagram</div> </div> <div style="padding: 12.5% 0;"></div> <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; margin-bottom: 14px; align-items: center;"> <div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(7px);"></div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; height: 12.5px; transform: rotate(-45deg) translateX(3px) translateY(1px); width: 12.5px; flex-grow: 0; margin-right: 14px; margin-left: 2px;"></div> <div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);"></div> </div> <div style="margin-left: 8px;"> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div> <div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)"></div> </div> <div style="margin-left: auto;"> <div style=" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div> <div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div> <div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div> </div> </div> <p></a> </p> <p style=" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;"> <a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BpPk6ailwXC/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_medium=loading" style=" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;" target="_blank">Fot. Marcin Zaborowski (@marcin.zaborowski ), fotograf National Geographic Polska @natgeopl &#8230; Na zdjƒôciu: Ida &#8230; Sesja portretowa w ramach kampanii spo≈Çecznej &#34;Popatrz na nas trochƒô inaczej&#34;, realizowanej na rzecz integracji oraz zapobiegania dyskryminacji os√≥b niepe≈Çnosprawnych. &#8230; @natgeopl @canonpolska @trocheinaczejpl #portret #kolor #look #portraitphotography #session #model #portrait #instapic #picoftheday #szczecin @quadralite #studio</a></p> <p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;">A post shared by <a target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/natgeopl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_medium=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;" target="_blank"> National Geographic Polska</a> (@natgeopl) on <time style=" font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;" datetime="2018-10-22T17:14:34+00:00">Oct 22, 2018 at 10:14am PDT</time></p> </div> </blockquote> <h3><b>Thinking differently about disability</b></h3> <p>The campaign &#8220;Look at us a little differently&#8221; is an initiative of the Association of Families and Friends of Children with Down Syndrome, or &#8220;Iskierka,&#8221; in Szczecin, Poland.</p> <p>The association makes sure that Down syndrome and autism are not associated with suffering and unhappiness. On their website, there are stories of people demonstrating that these conditions are not the end of the world, but rather the start of another, equally full and happy, life.</p> <p>Instead of fear and prejudice, they offer smiles and openness to others. And looking at the happy faces in Zaborowski&#8217;s photos, it&#8217;s hard not to see that in the beautiful people who agreed to be part of the campaign. They hope that maybe they can help to reduce discrimination against  people with different abilities and give their families and friends courage and support.</p> <p><fb:post target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/zaborowskiphotography/photos/a.575665329118664/2159930517358796/?type=3" data-width="552"></fb:post></p> <div class="bkreadmore"> <img width="150" height="75" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/res.cloudinary.com/aleteia/image/fetch/c_fill,g_auto,w_150,h_75/c_fill/c_fit,g_south_west,x_5,y_5,l_gallery_overlay_icon,o_50,w_55/https://aleteiaen.files.wordpress.com/2018/09/web3-changing-the-world-down-syndrome-facebook.jpg%3Fw%3D1200?ssl=1" /> <div class="text-container-with-image"> <div class="read-more"><em>Read more:</em></div> <a href="http://aleteia.org/2018/09/25/9-people-with-down-syndrome-who-are-changing-the-world/">  <strong>9 People with Down syndrome who are changing the world</strong></a> </div></div> <div class="bkreadmore"> <img width="150" height="75" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/res.cloudinary.com/aleteia/image/fetch/c_fill,g_auto,w_150,h_75/https://aleteiaen.files.wordpress.com/2018/09/web3-madeline-stuart-fashion-model-designer-down-syndrome-madeline-stuart-via-facebook-fair-use.jpg%3Fw%3D1200?ssl=1" /> <div class="text-container-with-image"> <div class="read-more"><em>Read more:</em></div> <a href="http://aleteia.org/2018/09/21/meet-an-international-supermodel-with-down-syndrome/">  <strong>Meet an international supermodel with Down syndrome</strong></a> </div></div> ";s:10:"post_title";s:77:"National Geographic's new photo campaign highlights people with Down Syndrome";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"pos